briefdescription.para: Derived types can invoke OnResourceRegistered to fire this event.
Derived types can invoke OnResourceParsed to fire this event.
Derived types can invoke OnResourceDisposed to fire this event.

parameterdescription.para: Takes as arguments the resource uri and the source text.

briefdescription.para: Expected to be concurrency safe with DisposeResource.
Provides syntax highlighting from the lexing result. This method is invoked, and applied, before GetSymbolsFor.
Provides syntax highlighting that cannot be determined by lexing alone. This method is invoked, and applied, after GetTokenTextSpansFor.
Provides 'squigglies' which when hovered over display a message, along with a serverity level.
Expected to be an Microsoft.Extensions.Hosting.IHostedService (or anything which performs background task work).
(2024-01-28) Goal: track the cursor's position within the compilation unit as it moves.
When a user types a period ('.') or hits the keybind: { 'Ctrl' + 'Space' } this method is invoked to populate the autocomplete menu.
Expected to be concurrency safe with RegisterResource.
A method wrapper for ResourceRegistered as to allow dervied types to invoke the event.
A method wrapper for ResourceParsed as to allow dervied types to invoke the event.
A method wrapper for ResourceDisposed as to allow derived types to invoke the event.
